Everyone on a team of 6 gets a (few) potion effect(s):
Strength: strength 1
Speed: speed 2, haste 2
Health: 10 extra hearts
Jump: jump boost 4, saturation, haste 2, no fall damage
Invis: invisibilty, water breathing
Res: resistance 2, fire resistance

This skript uses variables from D4's team manager. Edits of D4's skript will probably work too.

Commands:
Operators only:
/superheroes set    - Sets the superheroes for each team
/superheroes apply  - Applies effects
/superheroes reset  - Resets superheroes
